to Tanzania on safari,

00:39:59.440 --> 00:40:02.230
thinking that it's one of
the better run countries

00:40:02.230 --> 00:40:05.732
and the concept of
family and ujumaa.

00:40:05.732 --> 00:40:07.315
So I mean, what are
some good examples

00:40:07.315 --> 00:40:08.866
