00:48:12.640 --> 00:48:15.750
That's one of the downsides.

00:48:15.750 --> 00:48:17.885
There are these great
disparities of wealth,

00:48:17.885 --> 00:48:19.260
and there's a lot
of poor people.

00:48:19.260 --> 00:48:24.210
