hardcore violent crime,

00:48:24.210 --> 00:48:27.390
but there's still home
invasions and carjackings.

00:48:27.390 --> 00:48:31.830
But it's usually not gratuitous.

00:48:31.830 --> 00:48:34.230
So we have these guards
