SPEAKER: Well, that's all
we have time for today,

00:58:18.415 --> 00:58:19.956
but thank you so
much for joining us.

00:58:19.956 --> 00:58:21.500
Stick around for a
copy of the book,

00:58:21.500 --> 00:58:23.900
and give him a big
round of applause.

